Eyes over here, Spike.

7
00:00:12,700 --> 00:00:13,790
Uh, sorry.

8
00:00:13,830 --> 00:00:15,080
For this to work,
it's crucial

9
00:00:15,120 --> 00:00:17,000
we keep our concentration
totally on the --

10
00:00:17,040 --> 00:00:18,250
[ Poof! Strike! ]

11
00:00:18,250 --> 00:00:19,800
Ugh!

12
00:00:19,840 --> 00:00:20,920
[ Tweet! ]
Spike...

13
00:00:20,960 --> 00:00:23,800
This magic needs our full
attention to make it happen.

14
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:24,930
There's no other way.

15
00:00:24,970 --> 00:00:25,970
I can't help it!

16
00:00:26,010 --> 00:00:27,260
[ Zip! Zip! Boing! ]
Look!

17
00:00:27,300 --> 00:00:28,970
[ Zip! ]

18
00:00:29,010 --> 00:00:30,220
[ Patter! ]

19
00:00:30,260 --> 00:00:31,970
[ Zip! Blink! ]

20
00:00:31,970 --> 00:00:33,680
[ Sloop! Zip! ]

21
00:00:33,730 --> 00:00:35,140
[ Zip! ]

22
00:00:35,190 --> 00:00:36,770
[ Creak! ]

23
00:00:36,810 --> 00:00:38,150
[ Zip! ]

24
00:00:38,190 --> 00:00:39,900
[ Sighs ]
Never mind her.

25
00:00:39,940 --> 00:00:41,780
She's just being
Pinkie Pie.

26
00:00:41,820 --> 00:00:44,030
Super extra Pinkie Pie
today.

27
00:00:44,070 --> 00:00:45,780
[ Pitter! ]

28
00:00:45,820 --> 00:00:47,280
[ Rattle! ]

29
00:00:47,280 --> 00:00:48,570
[ Sighs ]

30
00:00:48,620 --> 00:00:50,910
Twitchy-twitch,
a-twitch-a-twitch!

31
00:00:50,950 --> 00:00:53,660
Pinkie Pie, what in the wide,
wide world of Equestria

32
00:00:53,700 --> 00:00:54,870
are you up to?

33
00:00:54,910 --> 00:00:56,750
Oh, it's my tail!
It's my tail!

34
00:00:56,790 --> 00:00:58,000
It's a-twitch-a-twitchin'!

35
00:00:58,040 --> 00:00:59,750
And you know
what that means.

36
00:00:59,790 --> 00:01:02,800
Actually, Pinkie,
I haven't the slightest idea.

37
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:05,130
The twitching means
my Pinkie sense is telling me

38
00:01:05,170 --> 00:01:06,970
that stuff's
gonna start falling!

39
00:01:07,010 --> 00:01:08,680
You two
better duck for cover!

40
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:10,300
Oh, Pinkie,
it's not gonna rain.

41
00:01:10,350 --> 00:01:12,890
Why, there's barely even
a cloud in the -- Ugh!

42
00:01:14,600 --> 00:01:15,350
[ Croaks ]

43
00:01:15,390 --> 00:01:18,600
He just said, "nice catch"
in frog.

44
00:01:18,650 --> 00:01:20,190
[ Croaks ]

